strings: <se_def>Coconut: Hi Jan, how are you doing? Is there a boat available?
<se_low>January: Meaning<:> good! But have you heard about Tsukikage Chen?
<se_def>Coconut: tea rose? Well, I heard that there is a treasure in Akanta called this.
<se_low>January: You are absolutely correct! After that, go to Escantaro. see you later!
